Requestments

- Bottle (0.8)
- PyYaml (inclued 3.08)
- PIL    (for resize tools)

Installation

- Create folder named "static/works"
- Copy tools/default-info.yaml to "static/works"
- Type command "python index.py"
- Browser http://localhost:8081/

Resize Tools

- Copy resize.py to root folder
- Create folder named 1 ... N
- Put captured screen to folder and named 1 ... N
- Then type the command "python resize.py"
  - It will create two image automatically
    1. 300 x 150 (named: thumb_*)
    2. 750 x auto height (named: 1 ... N)